That's the challenge.

00:41:26.387 --> 00:41:27.387
Attorney Park.

00:41:29.587 --> 00:41:32.757
You're worried about that letter he sent
to the witnesses, aren't you?

00:41:33.487 --> 00:41:34.497
Yes.

