00:42:01.587 --> 00:42:02.587
Sure, sounds good.

00:42:03.017 --> 00:42:05.687
I'd much rather pull an all-nighter
than just be on copy duty.

00:42:05.857 --> 00:42:09.057
So, should I finally show you
what I'm made of?

00:42:28.017 --> 00:42:31.047
- Thanks for all your hard work.
- Good job.

00:42:31.417 --> 00:42:32.417
- Bye.
- See you later.

00:42:45.967 --> 00:42:49.237
Today is the 4th hearing of the 1st trial
of the Lee Woo Gyeom case.

00:42:49.437 --> 00:42:52.437
The focus of this trial
is expected to be...

00:42:52.437 --> 00:42:55.237
on the witnesses' testimony
about the treatment.

